Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.45,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}「人とは違う」で差をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}コンビニの雑誌コーナー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}表紙にふとして書いてあった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:21.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}子供の頃は気にもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:24.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}気に入らなければ怒って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:27.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}好きなものを好きだと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:30.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕らは変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}守りたいものが変わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されない宝物から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:39.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されるための建前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:44.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}大人になるほど　後悔する生き物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}でもね　それでもね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}見えるものがあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}だから僕は僕らしく　そして君は君らしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:04.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}初めから　探すようなものではないんだと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.90,0:03:10.17,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕は君じゃないし　君も僕じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}すれ違う　手をつなぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:17.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}そこには愛だって生まれる　そういうもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:21.55,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:27.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変えられない　大切があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:31.42,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変わりゆく生活が　正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:08.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling wide to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:14.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:25.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}But it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:35.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:43.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the times we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:51.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}That the words in our hands we will draw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:59.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Maybe it wasn't 'cause\N you're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:11.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Every moment, everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:16.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can feel, I can feel
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:21.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding you from bad
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.68,0:22:28.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You will learn
